value.string: UIChanges-1
Firefox
n
UIC-1
Install SSE 10 on Windows / Unix machine.
The URL filtering page should display a new checkbox control Enable URL filtering and download of URL definitions.
Install appropriate AV and URL license.
Open a new browser instance and enter the SSE UI url.
Navigate to the SSE UI -> Policies -> Filtering -> URL tab page.
Check the URL tab for changes.

UIC-2
Install SSE 10 on Windows / Unix machine.
The checbox control should be enabled. The user should be able to select /de-select the URL filtering option by clicking on the control.
Install appropriate AV and URL license.
Open a new browser instance and enter the SSE UI url.
Navigate to the SSE UI -> Policies -> Filtering -> URL tab page.
Check the Enable URL filtering and download of URL definitions checkbox control on the URL tab.

Check that the URL tab displays radio button control for Enable Audit Mode.
